ed prior to or concomitantly with high dosages of methotrexate, such as those used to treat osteosarcoma.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/10331/', '', 'Golimumab, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Abatacept, Siponimod, More', 'Ritodrine, Bremelanotide, Flibanserin, Cabergoline, Bromocriptine, Ubidecarenone, Regadenoson, Ranolazine, Ivabradine, Chondroitin sulfate, Glucosamine, More', 1767369485);
